# Test API Endpoints

### Submit a new service request
POST http://localhost:5000/api/service-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "isCustomer": "yes",
  "subject": "Email Setup Help",
  "message": "I need help setting up my email on my iPhone."
}

### Get all service requests (admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/service-requests

### Get a specific service request (admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/service-requests/1

### Update service request status (admin)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/service-requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Health check
GET http://localhost:5000/health
